name: df-gzreg
body: |- wceq(cgzg, co(cgox(c1o, co(c1o, cgoe, emptycls)), cgoi, cgox(c1o, co(co(c1o, cgoe, emptycls), cgoa, cgol(c2o, co(co(c2o, cgoe, c1o), cgoi, cgon(co(c2o, cgoe, emptycls))))))))
comment: The Godel-set version of the Axiom of Regularity. (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 14-Jul-2013.)
